Detects Lazarus-style fileless execution, heavy PowerShell usage, and script-based payload delivery.


index=endpoint OR index=sysmon
(
    Image="*powershell.exe"
    OR CommandLine="*IEX*"
    OR CommandLine="*DownloadString*"
    OR CommandLine="*Net.WebClient*"
)
| stats count values(CommandLine) as cmd by host user src_ip
| where count > 3
| sort - count
